channel.title: Eohr - Snow Mountain [modern-irish jig // geometry dash type dance track]
channel.description:
so i made something out of a jig i wrote...
I've been involved with the traditional music scene and played fiddle for a long time but I decided now to combine this modern Irish folk-inspired tune with a dance beat and a drop I had laying around. Also I was in the vicinity of a mountain literally called "Snow Mountain" so I named it that.
https://soundcloud.com/eohr/snow-mountain
